        <div xml:id="AN19-kilavi"></div>
        <div xml:id="AN19">
            <lg type="edition"><l>aṉṟava <supplied>ḷo</supplied>ḻintaṉṟu milaiyē vantunaṉi</l>
<l>varuntiṉai <choice><seg>vāḻiye</seg><seg>vāḻiyeṉ</seg></choice> ṉeñcē paruntirun</l>
<l>tuyāviḷi payiṟṟu mayāvuyar naṉantalai</l>
<l>yuru<supplied>ṭu</supplied>ṭi makuḷiyiṟ poruṭerin <choice><seg>ticaikkuṅ</seg><seg>tiraikkuṅ</seg></choice></l>
<l>kaṭuṅkuraṟ kuṭiñaiya neṭumperuṅ kuṉṟa</l>
<l>memmō ṭiṟattaluñ <choice><seg>cellāy</seg><seg>ceyyāy</seg></choice> piṉṉiṉ</l>
<l>ṟoḻiyac cūḻntaṉai yāyiṟ ṟavirātu</l>
<l>celliṉic ciṟakkaniṉ ṉuḷḷam vallē</l>
<l>maṟava lōmpumati yemmē naṟaviṉ</l>
<l>cēyita ḻaṉaiya vākik kuvaḷai</l>
<l>māyitaḻ puraiyu <choice><seg>malirko</seg><seg>malirkō</seg></choice> <choice><seg>ḷīrimai</seg><seg>ḷiṇarimai</seg></choice></l>
<l><choice><seg>yuḷḷakaṅ</seg><seg>yuḷḷaṅ</seg></choice> kaṉala <supplied>vu</supplied>ḷḷutō ṟulaṟip</l>
<l>paḻaṅkaṇ koṇṭa <choice><seg>kataḻntuvī</seg><seg>kaliḻntuvī</seg></choice> ḻaviraṟal</l>
<l>veyya vukutara verīip paiyeṉac</l>
<l>cilvaḷai corinta melliṟai muṉkai</l>
<l><choice><seg>pūvī</seg><seg>pūvīya</seg></choice> koṭiyiṟ pulleṉap pōki</l>
<l>yaṭarce <choice><seg>yāyakaṟ</seg><seg>yātaṟ</seg></choice> cuṭartuṇai yāka</l>
<l>viyaṅkātu <choice><seg>vatintanaṅ</seg><seg>vatintaveṅ</seg></choice> kātali</l>
<l>yuyaṅkucāy ciṟupuṟa muyaṅkiya piṉṉē.</l></lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>That day there was no staying behind with her. Coming [along],</l>
<l>you suffered much, oh heart,</l>
<l rend="indent">	and the <choice><seg>langorous </seg><seg>langurous </seg></choice> high vast area,</l>
<l><choice><seg>	where </seg><seg>	where the </seg></choice> kites perch [and] repeat [their] dolorous shrieks,</l>
<l>the long big hills of the fierce-voiced horned <choice><seg>owls</seg><seg>owls,</seg></choice> </l>
<l rend="indent">	that <choice><seg>sound, </seg><seg>cry out, </seg></choice> <choice><seg>the meaning being clear, like the sound of a </seg><seg>the meaning being clear, like the sound of </seg></choice> turned hour-glass drum,</l>
<l>you <choice><seg>cannot </seg><seg>did not </seg></choice> traverse with us.</l>
<l rend="indent">	If, standing behind [us]</l>
<l>you have considered staying behind, without restraint</l>
<l>go now. <choice><seg>May </seg><seg>Let </seg></choice> your mind<note place="foot">The surprising bit is not the address to the heart that wants to go back to the beloved at home, but the fact that the heart, in its turn, is attributed with an uḷḷam, a mind of its own, as is confirmed by the gloss of the old commentary: neñciṉatu uḷḷam.</note> be strongly exulted.</l>
<l>Beware of forgetting <choice><seg>us</seg><seg>us –</seg></choice> </l>
<l><choice><seg>– </seg><seg></seg></choice> after you have embraced the small of the weakening, emaciated back</l>
<l>of our love who abides without stirring,</l>
<l rend="indent">	as a companion <choice><seg>[only] the glow of the choice earthern lamp, </seg><seg>the light emerging when </seg></choice> made <choice><seg>into </seg><seg>onto </seg></choice> a plate(?),</l>
<l>moving futily, like a creeper when [its] flowers perish,</l>
<l>with [her] soft-jointed <choice><seg>forearms </seg><seg>forearm </seg></choice> from which the few bangles slip <choice><seg>down</seg><seg>down,</seg></choice> </l>
<l>softly, frightened so that hot [tears] are shed,</l>
<l><choice><seg>	fast-descending </seg><seg>	brightly descending </seg></choice> shining <choice><seg>waters </seg><seg>water </seg></choice> holding [her] distress,</l>
<l>whithering whenever she remembers, while <choice><seg>she burns </seg><seg>[her] </seg></choice> <choice><seg>inside,</seg><seg>inside burns,</seg></choice> </l>
<l><choice><seg>[her] wet </seg><seg>[her] </seg></choice> <choice><seg>eye-lids being </seg><seg>eye-lids </seg></choice> <choice><seg>flooded, </seg><seg>flooded flower-clusters, </seg></choice> resembling the huge petals</l>
<l rend="indent">	of the blue water-lily, being as if they were the red petals of Naṟavu.</l></lg>
        </div>
    </body>
